title: Maytag Dishwasher Dishrack Adjuster and Wheel Assembly
description: Maytag Dishwasher Dishrack Adjuster and Wheel Assembly ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 14 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11756470 Manufacturer Part Number WPW10571738 This dishrack adjuster and wheel assembly is for dishwashers and lets you adjust the dishrack height and attaches the track wheels to the dishrack.

installationInstructions.author: Alfred L from WESTBOROUGH, MA
installationInstructions.title: The wheels on the bottom ‘basket’ are only fastened by a ‘Snap-in’ (plug) style connector that gets brittle and breaks over time
installationInstructions.content: Pop off the shell assembly from the bottom basket and clip/click on a new wheel assembly.
